    {
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Step through each colour:\n  R: ing2=R+ (ing2 has R+), ing5=R- (ing4+ing5=R-: both share R-)\n      \u2192 opposite signs \u2192 skip.\n  G: ing2=G- (ing2 G?: (sign undetermined)), ing5=G+ (ing5+ing8=G+: both share G+)\n      \u2192 opposite signs \u2192 skip.\n  B: ing2=B+ (ing2+ing4=B+: both share B+), ing5=B+ (ing5+ing7=B+: both share B+)\n      \u2192 SAME sign + \u2192 B+ resolves."
    },
